				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">RZ always spawns adds, it has nothing to do with deaths, it's part of the event.  I use a pet for this raid all the time (at the end), not for earlier stages however because of how many mobs ae dispel/ae ect.
<br />

<br />
Shei does spawn adds when she kills pets (When I lead raids for her I make it clear there are no pets/no swarm pets).
<br />

