				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Eandori. First, adds are from script, I'm certain.
<br />

<br />
Second, that epic pet phenomenon isn't entirely true. It's a taunt jump phenomena (MT can boost his aggro by taunting, and since epic pet has very high taunt/aggro, and warrior taunt will put him up to front of list, ahead of whatever the epic pet is, hence "taunt jump"), but if your tank that is tanking RZTW cannot hold aggro better then an epic pet, you have a problem to boot.<br />_________________<br />"The ability to quote is a serviceable substitute for wit."
